# nucleai Agent Instructions

This library uses runtime introspection. Use `import` and `help()` instead of searching files.

## Quick Start

```python
# Discover and explore
import nucleai
help(nucleai)                # Module overview
help(nucleai.simdb.query)    # Function docs with examples

# Get detailed info
from nucleai.core.introspect import get_function_signature
sig = get_function_signature(nucleai.simdb.query)
```

## Development

- Use `uv run` for all Python commands
- Python 3.13, modern syntax (`list[str]` not `List[str]`)
- Async with `anyio`, not asyncio
- Test with `pytest --cov` before committing

## Documentation

See `AGENT_QUICKSTART.md` for quick reference and `AGENTS.md` for complete guidelines.
